Our Solutions



      Descartes empowers companies to compete and thrive in today's new world of business with our logistics solutions including:    


 Logistics Technology Platform 
 The Logistics Technology Platform combines a network, applications, content, and a community. It is a comprehensive technology infrastructure that Descartes customers and their trading partners use to extend the command of their logistics operations.  
   

 Routing, Mobile, & Telematics 
 Routing, Mobile & Telematics: the most flexible and comprehensive suite of route planning, route execution and fleet/driver vehicle compliance and performance management solutions. 
   

 Transportation Management 
 Transportation Management: Broad and deep solutions for multimodal transportation planning, shipment and inventory management, carrier contract management, supplier/carrier performance management, freight auditing and logistics flow control to optimize and direct the movement of goods from order to receipt. 
   

 Customs & Global Trade Content 
 Customs & Global Trade Content: a comprehensive solution suite that provides advanced declaration capabilities, multimodal security filing for countries around the globe, and access to the world’s leading global trade content, denied party screening, cargo security and import/export trade data. 
   

 Global Logistics Network Services 
 Global Logistics Network Services: Helping logistics-oriented businesses connect, communicate and collaborate more efficiency via an inter-enterprise electronic data and document exchange. 
   

 Broker & Forwarder Enterprise Systems 
 Broker & Forwarder Enterprise Systems: domain rich back office solutions for shipment management, transportation bookings, security filings, customs entries, warehousing and financial businesses processes. 
   

 






 Our Logistics Technology Platform 
 Descartes Logistics Technology Platform accelerates time-to-value and increases the productivity and performance for businesses of all sizes. 
 Discover More  

 Our Applications 
 Descartes’ Logistics Application Suite offers the industry’s widest array of modular, cloud-based, interoperable web and wireless logistics applications. 
 Discover More  

 Our Network 
 Descartes Global Logistics Network™ is the standard for multimodal, inter-enterprise data exchange. 
 Ask Us More  

 Our Content 
 Descartes’ global trade content helps improve trade compliance, reduce risk, minimize duty spend, and gain insight into international trade. 
 Discover More  

 Our Community 
 The world’s largest multimodal logistics community enabling companies to quickly connect and collaborate. 
 Learn More  

 






