Working with leading retailers around the globe, Descartes has developed real-time integrated route planning and mobility solutions to enable retailers to grow revenue, increase margins and provide differentiated customer service. These home delivery solutions are unique in that they include three important elements...


Glossary: Logistics and Supply Chain Management


Logistics and supply chain management glossary of terms.


MAP-21: A New Day Dawning?


“Moving Ahead for Progress in the 21st Century” Act, better known as “MAP-21.” The law funded the nation’s highway and mass transit projects for 27 months at a cost of $105 billion. It placed unprecedented emphasis on freight movement and recognized freight’s importance to the economy. 
